{"h6a75aea6gce9cg45a7gb837g9d94d2a3e121": ["What's wrong with you? Let her go!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "9fa93369-08ca-e22b-d70a-0621b917b81e"], "h2d18b9c4g588ag4333gb46fgbeb02d9ef43f": ["You're a medium! You're going to speak to her.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "c59b079e-8696-8d9e-99d6-abd22fa658cc"], "h9d3f6e5egc283g447fg8cb4g7a983cb37344": ["Could you ask her something for me?", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "ca7ba6a9-5ac3-8b14-6dcc-fad10ce7ff22"], "h845e5e1bgc49eg4055gbd80g0fff59688613": ["I can't. She won't answer any more questions.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "c3dc604a-c8ff-11ed-db2a-0c93c90cd64f"], "h82e676efg01bdg44dbgbd18gea5e5b21ebca": ["Oh. It was probably pointless anyway.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "4b97efff-f03f-61c8-cf0a-2c7a3c17e31e"], "hf353fde4g32b8g4036g8b84g7d819a09f637": ["I'd hoped she could tell us where she took the dowry.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "d28da176-0f61-2b06-ccfb-ee3b45c9a543"], "ha5e12d00gb8f8g46b1g985egde2a3421eebb": ["I'll look around. Any idea where it's stashed?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "8e0324cb-18ea-4186-7ce3-09021c2f3811"], "h7c669c09g2f7cg4079gae1ageaef296ed059": ["She didn't make it far. It'll be close.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "523eb333-9cc5-0328-444f-8c98f141a4f5"], "hb0b5e1e1g0762g4776ga5b1g07c97e435a4f": ["Stop worrying about the dowry. It's gone.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "acbe63be-b023-25b4-e035-dd65af6af575"], "h44684ce7ga0d7g43f6gb63dg6f9266b06009": ["No, you're right. Those monsters could've taken it.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "c746af6c-240e-e662-2677-024f79479f64"], "hcaa9fa37g91b1g4b76gb9b4gb3f155cb0885": ["She had her sister's dowry. I'd hoped she could tell us where it is.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "4089352d-1b63-350a-b77f-1a1818189e22"], "hc116b81fgee8dg49f7gaa6fg018ceb7b6edd": ["Maybe. What do you want me to ask?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "0b1a228d-2bd1-11ae-ea68-cb6d9a9e94e2"], "hcf94e540gbdb1g45c4ga446gc87562ae89ae": ["The dowry. She'd know where it is.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "78ef4d1f-aeef-7dad-c36b-d719ea78d3ac"], "h95232189gbed2g46c5gb6e3gdd38d3893109": ["It's for her sister's wedding. Miri had it when she ran out. ", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "0594107a-eed7-5bf5-16b7-2ebb0091d48e"], "hcedc742dg4115g4317gbc7cga07e80b70eca": ["This dowry? I'm keeping it as payment for saving your life", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "e90b9523-27c9-c2c4-11b8-a398c0df6958"], "hb1c5f6ecga18cg40c4g92b1g5c9a6bebc048": ["You... what?", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "99461c01-dcf2-6c52-669c-9a2b135340e8"], "h45d16b7fge1cdg41c5ga5d1g1c07aaf12a1e": ["Fine. I hope you choke on it.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "ec7577ca-f20d-1cf2-1bd2-2bf6605f0e79"], "h9f65708bgd154g4edega308g597eb4afeb05": ["Let her go. And go to hell.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "bdd791b3-2b5a-407a-2dac-43cf83879016"], "h7b5c338cgb744g42bbgad47gddab445652be": ["*The corpse regards you lifelessly.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "1fbcaa9b-a821-20d5-f791-48d3fdb41d2e"], "hcb63c42fg29adg48d1ga804g963356b9adeb": ["I already found it. Here, take it. ([GEN_CheckMagicPocketGold_6057ad05-9492-4630-9f0a-be548b134c54])", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "702957e8-e220-5949-7577-9df5c56cdfd0"], "h77d67728g8468g4220g9ceagbd6bc486276c": ["I know this doesn't change anything, but it helps. Thank you.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "a3cb4df8-8d19-b0fa-8aac-dff967879592"], "hbe6ad4aagf6d3g4422g9008gaf7f94fa0eeb": ["You can stop now. Let her rest.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "38b0d0b9-8b99-bdef-0268-06f069d59f9b"], "hf910e606g6c9fg43d0g86c8g8982219afde3": ["I already know where it is.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "1197258d-20a5-d040-e8fb-f5b4d5a1887c"], "hd2ff9773gca75g42cagb7cbg25f66090784f": ["I trust you to get it for me. I can't leave her.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "800c0d18-209d-3a39-11ac-c098b1158d2c"], "hc90997dcgce4ag441fgaa2dg618bf8099735": ["<i>Ask his question.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "7597efca-1c21-e4f5-4987-555420a03214"], "hf073631dgb3fdg4b76g9ba0gba2a3fa188cb": ["... dowry... for sister... in barn...", "1ed658d0-e88a-4b7b-ab9e-1e520ae7d0c7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "6a3fa909-b0bf-7f12-1770-fe62be50e82a"], "he4987903gbe39g4f44gb2acgd98ddcd27d39": ["The barn? She must mean one of the empty buildings behind the inn.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "6fda0b2f-b336-673c-8ba7-ed97a025a5cf"], "hd8d53245gf610g41a9gaefegf46c0e7d2a14": ["I've done enough for you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "1efbb16a-8372-0ce8-0087-222fb7ad13be"], "h7486ebe6gc06ag432dg9d77g4ae0463aa7a6": ["Heartless bastard... let her go!", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "a9423dde-71bf-d43a-39e2-4820d806de04"], "hc7cbd089g07a5g42c6g862ag2bd49dccbf72": ["Be quiet. I have questions of my own.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "76106b9e-4c5e-5e44-06a3-b8aad7129e06"], "h8fa87c24gb5bdg4c6egbbc4g190158c3ef74": ["Please.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "371a47ee-bacd-d0ff-c97a-8a85db797c60"], "hae7e5ea5ge5f2g4292g902dge222d31451f8": ["I said no.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "657de5db-786c-a743-a5dd-ae57108a28a9"], "h5b008005gd31bg4b44gac96g1866b3b75a61": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "ebd9c9bc-2e96-bd4b-41bc-50da0f4ff135"], "hc8008b7fgbe90g4647ga02ega50724eae4c5": ["Please, leave her be. She deserves peace.", "5fcc3167-5a0c-41e7-b44c-d629d34370cb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "453aec00-6734-75c5-e8d9-22ad2f144d42"], "h6d3b8205gb9a2g47f0gaef0g7087ad641af3": ["Who are you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "04129d58-29f2-0af2-6f6b-ceb4005a7de8"], "h57a20d33ge9dfg4eceg8e84g6f29e1053ef6": ["... Mirileth... farmer...", "1ed658d0-e88a-4b7b-ab9e-1e520ae7d0c7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "f8f7de0a-cde9-26aa-7fed-590ec30021fd"], "h1285b12cg6b93g42b5gac49gd4809117f273": ["Why were you at the inn?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "d02979e0-52e1-931d-6133-a98b00d77f39"], "hd6656bfag5b65g4bb4ga43ag73b12278f72b": ["... from Elturgard... travelling... sister's wedding...", "1ed658d0-e88a-4b7b-ab9e-1e520ae7d0c7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "fe02fbbe-fb4a-2341-2258-f0d06271dfcd"], "h9fa730dfg360bg44f3gb7cag3a3d89cd2ecd": ["How did you die?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "8ecef06b-6d2c-7c70-4b89-a34214846218"], "h5bf44bd5gc081g4902g8f52g391585ef2394": ["... finding... husband... Benryn... inside... ", "1ed658d0-e88a-4b7b-ab9e-1e520ae7d0c7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "3e6712fa-86e1-7b33-1dd6-2bbaf75b0353"], "h8b8c6678gaebfg44f9g8c75g206408886e00": ["... door... locked... trapped... fire...", "1ed658d0-e88a-4b7b-ab9e-1e520ae7d0c7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "d59576f7-3c0d-2b71-f11b-85f6f5cc5d27"], "h37c824begb2e8g4625g9e57ga0546c06848e": ["Where is Benryn?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "58bef2cf-c1cc-ad3c-98b9-46e69a8ac2b8"], "h846f4b82g17f9g4d74g8a95g9cb07a0b652f": ["... inside... room... top floor...", "1ed658d0-e88a-4b7b-ab9e-1e520ae7d0c7", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "949f956e-d44c-d5b2-c8a2-05d8cfaf39b2"], "h6cf5d095g6bb7g442bgb502g8f8e6179aa54": ["Did you have any valuables nearby?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "c27df6c7-090e-d4fc-2fb5-79e456753e4a"], "h4d438dbag8723g4232gb7d0g9cc6858c9536": ["Where is your sister's dowry?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "1384c395-b30e-956f-d47e-ff1ae069eb32"], "hacf2d7c7g7cdeg411fg9f1fgf6e14a08de76": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "9acbdb84-a0bc-b738-aab2-edd3fdda05b8"], "h547caa39gbca8g4b91gbc1eg6e79bb537622": ["*The spell's power wanes. You can ask no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "252e7566-851c-9979-b5b5-c330afd6dbf3"], "h83fd768ag94bag48c5gadf8g7404c5a0d8b6": ["*The corpse does not stir. It will answer no more questions.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_Tavern_DeadCiv1_Dead.html", "28e5d1f1-a5ae-760f-265e-e1c0299cf9a6"]}